DarkMouse::

She smirked and started walking down the ramp, wondering how long it 
would take for one of the bots to realize that she couldn't fly. If 
the matrix intended me to fly, it would have given me wings, she 
thought to herself. "god of neptune?" she muttered, wondering why 
anybot would think themselves a god. On the other hand, Megatron did 
just that, and he's still around, or so she thought. She ambled down 
the ramp in mouse mode, hoping to get a few good shot in and draw 
mech fluid before the day was out.  She smiled. it had been for what 
seemed like an eternity since she got into a good old fashioned dog 
fight with a maximal. She hoped her older fighting programs would 
hold out.
